\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {3}{\ignorespaces Inner loop of the ADMM solver, expanding the box labeled `ADMM solver' in Fig.\nobreakspace  {}2\hbox {}. The blue block is precomputed once at startup from the discretized dynamics and cost; the three red blocks are the per-iteration work, with steps (1)--(3) corresponding to equations (4\hbox {})--(6\hbox {}) in the text. Caching the Riccati recursion reduces step (1) from a $332{\times }332$ sparse Cholesky to an $n_x{\times }n_x$ matvec.}}{3}{}\protected@file@percent }
