\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {5}{\ignorespaces Closed-loop tracking on the figure-8 reference. The tuned C ADMM ($\rho {=}3$) holds steady-state RMSE at $3.42$\nobreakspace  {}mm; OSQP and ReLU-QP find essentially the same trajectory ($\approx 4.86$\nobreakspace  {}mm) since all three minimize the same constrained-LQR QP. Residual differences below $\sim 2$\nobreakspace  {}mm are dominated by hover-linearization error against the nonlinear MuJoCo simulation rather than by solver tolerance.}}{4}{}\protected@file@percent }
